neutral.headline: Trina Vega Spinoff 'Hollywood Arts' Starring Daniella Monet Moves To Netflix With Series Order And Cast Set; Nick & P+ Get Second Window - Deadline
neutral.body_html: The spinoff of the hit TV show ‘Victorious’, featuring Trina Vega as Hollywood Arts director and starring Daniella Monet is moving to Netflix with a series order. The cast also includes Nick E. Lee (Nick) & Peyton Parker (P+).

liberal.headline: Trina Vega Spinoff 'Hollywood Arts' Starring Daniella Monet Moves To Netflix With Series Order, Cast Set; Nick And P+ Get Second Window - Deadline
liberal.body_html: The spinoff of the hit TV show ‘Victorious’ is a big win for diversity in entertainment. The new series 'Hollywood Arts', starring Daniella Monet as Trina Vega, will move to Netflix with an order and cast set that includes Nick E. Lee (Nick) & Peyton Parker (P+). This development comes after a push by fans for more representation on screen.
